{"tid":1538220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"The Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act must be passed","createTime":"2019-09-04T06:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:43:02.000Z","uid":300592,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ab3721d44655b09b5ef059e6647fe26ab1e56c11","tid":1538220,"uid":300592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:40:07.000Z","msg":"Let&rsquo;s make it clear to the world:<br />\nThe Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act must be passed, even if Carrie Lam withdraws the extradition bill now!<br />\nAll five demands of the people of Hong Kong must be fulfilled! We won&rsquo;t give up and we have no room to compromise!"},{"pid":"f0610fa9931b956a70ddd271973cb6f064a20a14","tid":1538220,"uid":121869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mS3qqGn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmS3qqGn.jpg&h=e0db4b33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n熊家俊先生 (25歲) - 15/12/2017<br />\n梁凌杰先生 (35歲) - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐 (21歲) - 30/6/2019<br />\nZhita Wu (29歲) - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐 (28歲) - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生 (32歲) - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生 (26歲) - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生 (25歲) - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生 (16歲) - 2/9/2019<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n民族自強 港人自救<br />\n沒有暴徒 只有暴政<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\nFIVE DEMANDS - NOT ONE LESS"},{"pid":"baf41916ec1f9114e1d5df2b65f81b088001d6d2","tid":1538220,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cWEMUHb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWEMUHb.jpg&h=cc5ef0de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n入嚟幫手推<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n</span></span></strong> <br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a h